nodes.bodyText: not sure - maybe whitespace format? before '{'
statuses here are undefined, thus there are no labels for the milestones below.

nodes.bodyText: in graphql types.tsx I can see just available, active, completed. Terminated is not there.
I guess the comparison is based on the order in which values are defined in MilestoneStatus type?
the status values are probably not passed correctly, see the snapshot, it results in undefined, thus there's no value returned by handleStatus function.
